{"name": "nkdfu", "metadata": {"name": "nkdfu", "version": "0.2", "classifiers": ["Intended Audience :: Developers", "Intended Audience :: End Users/Desktop", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU General Public License v2 (GPLv2)", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3 :: Only", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7"], "home_page": "https://github.com/Nitrokey/nkdfu", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["fire", "tqdm", "intelhex", "libusb1"], "summary": "DFU tool for updating Nitrokeys' firmware", "upload_time": 1666796370}, "documentation": ["# Nitrokey DFU tool - nkdfu\n\n`nkdfu` is a Python DFU tool for updating Nitrokeys' firmware. Currently supports Nitrokey Pro only.\n\nBased on [python-dfu] project, which brings implementation of USB DFU 1.1 spec.\n\n## Call\n\n```\n$ nkdfu FIRMWARE_PATH <flags>\n```\n\nSee `nkdfu --help` for details.\n\n## Installation\n\n### From Repository\n\n```bash\n$ pip3 install nkdfu\n```\n\n\n### Directly from releases\nIt is possible to install it directly from the releases page:\n\n```bash\n$ pip3 install https://github.com/Nitrokey/nkdfu/releases/download/v0.1/nkdfu-0.1-py3-none-any.whl\n```\n\n## License\nLicense follows upstream - GPLv2. See [LICENSE] for details.\n\n\n[LICENSE]: ./LICENSE\n[python-dfu]: https://github.com/vpelletier/python-dfu"], "modules": [{"name": "nkdfu.dfu", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "nkdfu.dfu.getDFUDescriptor", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "usb_device", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Retrieve and parse a DFU descriptor from given device.\nusb_device\n    usb1.USBDevice instance.\n    Device will not be opened by this function.\nReturns a 6-tuple:\n    - attribute bitmask (see DFU_ATTRIBUTE_*)\n    - detach timeout (in ms)\n    - transfer size (in bytes)\n    - version number\n    - protocol (see DFU_PROTOCOL_*)\n    - USB interface number\n    - a list of usb descriptors for each DFU alternate setting on device\n      Useful for STM extension."]}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu._getNextSTMBlockNumber", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "blocknum", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu._getNextStandardBlockNumber", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "blocknum", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu._completeFieldLists", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu._parseFieldList", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "data", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "field_list", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu._generateFieldList", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "data_dict", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "field_list", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_REQUEST_TYPE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_DETACH", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_DNLOAD", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_UPLOAD", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_GETSTATUS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_CLRSTATUS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_GETSTATE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_ABORT", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_ST_SET_ADDRESS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_ST_ERASE_PAGE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_TIMEOUT", "type": null, "documentation": ["from dfuse-dfu-util"]}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_STATUS_DICT", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_STATE_APP_IDLE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "nkdfu.dfu.DFU_STATE_APP_DETACH",